    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2008 BMW M3 represents the peak of naturally aspirated M-division engineering, featuring the iconic S65 4.0L V8 mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The engine utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to provide razor-sharp throttle response, pulling cleanly to its 8,400 RPM redline. This example has been mechanically vetted, with proactive rod bearing and throttle actuator replacements already performed to ensure the integrity of the valvetrain and reciprocating assembly. The chassis remains composed with M-specific suspension geometry and a functional carbon fiber roof that significantly lowers the center of gravity. Equipped with an M Variable Differential Lock, this vehicle offers exceptional lateral grip and mechanical feedback, making it a highly capable driver\u2019s car in solid mechanical health.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
