    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the new-car price tag. It\u2019s clean, runs great, and is totally ready for its next adventure! I've taken good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great home. Come take it for a spin, I think you'll really love it!",
